{"tid":1053533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國人大代表建議 送貓熊給高雄 當韓國瑜到訪中國伴手禮","createTime":"2019-03-09T06:46:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T12:08:16.000Z","uid":35790,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ac877b59a77e9b4f8741cae9d01b5b0bb1e1d938","tid":1053533,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:46:21.000Z","msg":"大陸人大代表建議 送貓熊給高雄 當韓國瑜伴手禮<br />\n<br />\n2019-03-09 14:21聯合報 記者林則宏╱即時報導<br />\n<br />\n據《環球網》報導，大陸全國人大代表、全國台聯副會長許沛表示，她對高雄市長韓國瑜本月底將到廈門、深圳等地參訪表示歡迎。她同時期待韓國瑜未來也能來重慶交流，而「人要交流，動物也要交流」。因此，她將在今年兩會上建議：「向高雄市贈送大熊貓」，因為高雄有壽山動物園，這方面可以跟重慶做對接。<br />\n<br />\n許沛同時也是重慶市台聯會長，據香港中評社報導，許沛祖籍台灣台南，曾祖父許南英，曾是清代台灣33位科舉進士之一。許沛受訪時表示，自己每年還是會回台灣，多半跟著公務團來台灣，目前她在台南、台北、新竹等地都還有親戚，她已經大陸第三代台籍人士。<br />\n<br />\n報導稱，在今年大陸全國兩會上，許沛提出兩個建議，其中之一就是「向台灣高雄市贈送大熊貓的建議」。她表示，「人要交流，動物也要交流」，她正在努力做一些基礎的工作，希望把這個橋樑搭建起來，「這是非常有意義的事情」。<br />\n<br />\n許沛說，「韓市長確實應該看看大陸的變化」，雖然重慶跟高雄沒有直接對接，但希望高雄的壽山動物園，跟重慶的動物園「接一個對子」。<br />\n<br />\n對於韓國瑜即將到大陸參訪，許沛表示歡迎，她強調，「兩岸越走越親，應該要多走動」。<br />\n<br />\n對於韓國瑜將前往大陸參訪的含義，許沛認為，就是帶頭承認「92共識」，有引領的效應，能夠得到民眾的共識。<br />\n<br />\n不過，許沛也提到，韓國瑜此次到大陸參訪，必然會受到不少壓力，但她表示，「希望（韓國瑜）能夠堅強挺住，我們大陸13億的朋友為他挺住」。同時，她也歡迎台灣其他藍營執政縣市首長，都能多來大陸走走，「兩岸交流是必然，民進黨也應該擋不住的」。<br />\n&lt;聯合&gt;"},{"pid":"1a8671bca8fd755cdccc8fd15ef2e184fa2c03c2","tid":1053533,"uid":50457,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:50:04.000Z","msg":"每次&ldquo;送&rdquo;熊貓，每一個國家都要交年費<br />\n<br />\n實際上係出租熊貓"},{"pid":"23c84fe2731d48a656a50c08e7ca2e2d29b33fc4","tid":1053533,"uid":35790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:51:53.000Z","msg":"高雄發大財<br />\n出錢養熊貓"},{"pid":"f2ad7e2cef3f3ce343cf1ee63c2ddb397a09fa2e","tid":1053533,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:53:42.000Z","msg":"熊貓：屌！"},{"pid":"cae7885263042944f9e6029261c057180b549a96","tid":1053533,"uid":61271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T07:00:34.000Z","msg":"其實而家仲有人會想睇熊貓咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77696b788bcd222dc46882a12564bb8de7e51258","tid":1053533,"uid":48011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2ad7e2cef3f3ce343cf1ee63c2ddb397a09fa2e","tid":1053533,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T06:53:42.000Z","msg":"熊貓：屌！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T07:09:07.000Z","msg":"熊貓：又迫我扑野"},{"pid":"41467172fca3dd2fa46fb307c50a84061be91abc","tid":1053533,"uid":35430,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T07:11:17.000Z","msg":"高雄養多隻垃圾大食懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n交年費買竹又要保養專人照顧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2fd1a3cbb10f5014545143a3ab9cedd042f9517","tid":1053533,"uid":55231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T07:15:08.000Z","msg":"高雄窮到仆街仲要比錢養熊貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51030887397286aa9f1645db503eaa9b42197619","tid":1053533,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"41467172fca3dd2fa46fb307c50a84061be91abc","tid":1053533,"uid":35430,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T07:11:17.000Z","msg":"高雄養多隻垃圾大食懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n交年費買竹又要保養專人照顧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T07:17:47.000Z","msg":"上午飲酒 下午龜息"},{"pid":"9af845cb442964afab71cdc2ef5c5387a06b0373","tid":1053533,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T07:17:51.000Z","msg":"養都算<br />\n一間問你拎返&lsquo;租借費&rsquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e7826b26c245b84d5ae6d77ed437a1a4a7c5e18","tid":1053533,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51030887397286aa9f1645db503eaa9b42197619","tid":1053533,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"41467172fca3dd2fa46fb307c50a84061be91abc","tid":1053533,"uid":35430,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T07:11:17.000Z","msg":"高雄養多隻垃圾大食懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n交年費買竹又要保養專人照顧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T07:17:47.000Z","msg":"上午飲酒 下午龜息"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T07:20:25.000Z","msg":"中共收息<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec31ccffd4ba0c736c5e3301c4024a899b3ebd2","tid":1053533,"uid":40387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T07:22:06.000Z","msg":"我都好想有傻鳩做對手，輕輕鬆鬆就屌打佢"},{"pid":"744b444eda8a5e17678811c85389ae18e903ab3d","tid":1053533,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T07:23:18.000Z","msg":"嫌佢唔夠窮  仲想佢幫手養多隻大食懶"},{"pid":"afc4c6141974d87de1ae6756e24d082fafaed422","tid":1053533,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T07:24:01.000Z","msg":"高雄有咗熊貓就發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad78271806082efc07459e14d28d35e2abb078df","tid":1053533,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ec31ccffd4ba0c736c5e3301c4024a899b3ebd2","tid":1053533,"uid":40387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T07:22:06.000Z","msg":"我都好想有傻鳩做對手，輕輕鬆鬆就屌打佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T07:24:54.000Z","msg":"G持韓國瑜代表國民黨參選總統"},{"pid":"eb1b70bebf03dbf593fed6e731ad6b2d5c652e0d","tid":1053533,"uid":43428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T07:26:01.000Z","msg":"上年去台灣旅行 聽個導遊講<br />\n內地好似送左兩隻熊貓叫 團團 圓圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n台灣送返兩隻鹿 叫平平安安 <br />\n意思係我地好平安 唔好搞我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36378383b6fb517fe0a496d6d6dd85b8dbb1538","tid":1053533,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb1b70bebf03dbf593fed6e731ad6b2d5c652e0d","tid":1053533,"uid":43428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T07:26:01.000Z","msg":"上年去台灣旅行 聽個導遊講<br />\n內地好似送左兩隻熊貓叫 團團 圓圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n台灣送返兩隻鹿 叫平平安安 <br />\n意思係我地好平安 唔好搞我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T07:26:49.000Z","msg":"馬9攪出來"},{"pid":"f77e6662cba5d6049174341b4940c9c88a8f98d1","tid":1053533,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:34:28.000Z","msg":"太貴養不起　馬來西亞想把貓熊還給中國<br />\n<br />\n中國大陸國寶貓熊長相可愛，經常被北京當作外交工具租借給他國。但貓熊的租借費每年高達3千萬台幣，讓馬來西亞人大喊養不起，要求政府把貓熊送還給中國。<br />\n<br />\n中國為紀念和大馬建交40周年，於2014年5月將貓熊興興、靚靚送到馬國，在馬來西亞國家動物園飼養。興興和靚靚成功繁衍後代生下兩隻貓熊寶寶，其中一隻名叫暖暖的貓熊寶寶，依照協議已經還給中國大陸。<br />\n然當地媒體報導，民眾批評飼養貓熊實在太貴，要求把貓熊送還給中國。根據馬來西亞與中國的協議，一對貓熊的租金每年100萬美元（約3076萬元台幣），每隻貓熊保險費每年5萬令吉（約36.6萬元台幣）。當地國家動物園也說，貓熊館的收入在扣除每月營運成本、飼料費用、員工成本、保安和維修費成本後，難以負擔大熊貓租金和保險費。<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞水源、土地與天然資源部長賽維爾透露，政府耗資太多錢在飼養大熊貓上，引起人民強烈不滿，他會把這事帶到內閣討論。<br />\n<br />\n養大熊貓的花費：<br />\n●租金：一對貓熊每年100萬美元<br />\n●支持研究：取得貓熊進口資格，必要資助中國貓熊保護項目。同時投資進行貓熊研究，一年費用61萬美元（約1873萬元台幣），成果還要與中國分享。<br />\n●建造貓熊館：營造生活環境，300萬至500萬美元（約9217萬至1億5362萬元台幣）不等。<br />\n●貓熊寶寶：誕下之後向中國付60萬美元（約1843萬元台幣），3年後要送回中國。<br />\n●食物：貓熊每天進食12至38公斤食物，特別對竹子需求量很大，可能要空運或自行種植竹子，估計一年花費60萬元人民幣（約267.2萬元台幣）。<br />\n●員工、醫療：以美國的動物園為例，有400人種竹子，另有6名醫療人員，加上其他日常開支，一年花費50萬美元（約1536萬元台幣）。<br />\n●非正常死亡：若貓熊出現不測，如2010年日本神戶的貓熊龍龍，在麻醉時吸入嘔吐物窒息，日本要即時支付50萬美元。<br />\n（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181219/1486024/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181219%2F1486024%2F&d=i2Kzi6k%2Bo1XjTd2IKJX6uRyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=f62acb1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181219%2F1486024%2F&h=54f9644d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181219/1486024/</a>"},{"pid":"106738f945798ba90fe62c6bdff91f94def7070d","tid":1053533,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:36:30.000Z","msg":"仲有樣<br />\n高雄咁熱<br />\n熊貓要24小時開冷氣<br />\n一停電就好快死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9909936fbe39f9dd6b7800f1d23b22f9ab1a931b","tid":1053533,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f77e6662cba5d6049174341b4940c9c88a8f98d1","tid":1053533,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:34:28.000Z","msg":"太貴養不起　馬來西亞想把貓熊還給中國<br />\n<br />\n中國大陸國寶貓熊長相可愛，經常被北京當作外交工具租借給他國。但貓熊的租借費每年高達3千萬台幣，讓馬來西亞人大喊養不起，要求政府把貓熊送還給中國。<br />\n<br />\n中國為紀念和大馬建交40周年，於2014年5月將貓熊興興、靚靚送到馬國，在馬來西亞國家動物園飼養。興興和靚靚成功繁衍後代生下兩隻貓熊寶寶，其中一隻名叫暖暖的貓熊寶寶，依照協議已經還給中國大陸。<br />\n然當地媒體報導，民眾批評飼養貓熊實在太貴，要求把貓熊送還給中國。根據馬來西亞與中國的協議，一對貓熊的租金每年100萬美元（約3076萬元台幣），每隻貓熊保險費每年5萬令吉（約36.6萬元台幣）。當地國家動物園也說，貓熊館的收入在扣除每月營運成本、飼料費用、員工成本、保安和維修費成本後，難以負擔大熊貓租金和保險費。<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞水源、土地與天然資源部長賽維爾透露，政府耗資太多錢在飼養大熊貓上，引起人民強烈不滿，他會把這事帶到內閣討論。<br />\n<br />\n養大熊貓的花費：<br />\n●租金：一對貓熊每年100萬美元<br />\n●支持研究：取得貓熊進口資格，必要資助中國貓熊保護項目。同時投資進行貓熊研究，一年費用61萬美元（約1873萬元台幣），成果還要與中國分享。<br />\n●建造貓熊館：營造生活環境，300萬至500萬美元（約9217萬至1億5362萬元台幣）不等。<br />\n●貓熊寶寶：誕下之後向中國付60萬美元（約1843萬元台幣），3年後要送回中國。<br />\n●食物：貓熊每天進食12至38公斤食物，特別對竹子需求量很大，可能要空運或自行種植竹子，估計一年花費60萬元人民幣（約267.2萬元台幣）。<br />\n●員工、醫療：以美國的動物園為例，有400人種竹子，另有6名醫療人員，加上其他日常開支，一年花費50萬美元（約1536萬元台幣）。<br />\n●非正常死亡：若貓熊出現不測，如2010年日本神戶的貓熊龍龍，在麻醉時吸入嘔吐物窒息，日本要即時支付50萬美元。<br />\n（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181219/1486024/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=htt